query:

  (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(countryCode) FROM supplierCoverageCountries WHERE supplierId = 240001) as coverage_countries,
  (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT countryCode) FROM supplierRates WHERE supplierId = 240001) as rate_countries
